Directed by Prakash Kovelamudi.

Written by Kanika Dhillon.

Cast Kangana Ranaut(Bobby Batliwala Garewal). Rajkummar Rao(Keshav / Shravan). Amyra Dastur(Reema). Amrita Puri(Megha). Jimmy Shergill(Shridhar (as Jimmy Sheirgill)) . Karan Ashar(Factory Manager). Backagaindancer(Jimmy). Dev Barot(Dancer). Lalit Behl(Uncle). Tina Chandorkar(Indian Police Inspector Pandey). Hussain Dalal(Varun). Prayag Damle(Doctor). Debtosh Darjee(Hanuman / Ward Boy). Kanika Dhillon(Sita). Jay Gandhi(Sound Engineer). Allan Hopwood(Taxi Driver). Brijendra Kala(Constable Ravi Dubey). Satish Kaushik(Inspector Dayanand). Richard Bhakti Klein(Hospital Psychiatrist (as R. Bhakti Klein)). Jeff Mirza(Music director). Aarav Mishra(Ambulance). Madhurima Roy(Shanaya). Joanna Shegera(Ballerina). Monica Wadwa(Zara). Dave Watts(British Policeman PC Watts). Shubhankar Das(Fellow accused at the court (uncredited)). Viktorija Faith(Clubber (uncredited)). Steven Pereira(Paramedic (uncredited)). Karl-Martin Rantapelkonen(Self – Restaurant guest (uncredited)). Shakti Rawal(Senior Officer (uncredited)). RoksolanaHasekiHÃ¼rrem(Party girl (uncredited)). Shreyas Shah(Lord Ram / Spiritual messenger (uncredited)). Anup Sharma(Young Kangana’s Father (uncredited)). Richa Tiwari(News Anchor (uncredited))

Language Hindi.

Producers Sankalp Acharekar. Ekta Kapoor. Shobha Kapoor. Sunil Dolamani Panda. Virral Patel. Ajay Rai. Ruchikaa Kapoor Sheikh. Shaailesh R Singh. Ssunny Suraani. Hitesh Thakkar. Alok Tripathi. Sarmad Varraich.

Production Balaji Motion Pictures.
